OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,7,FBonner has been speaking to some of
OL,8,Fthe people involved in trying to
OL,9,Fresurrect the building.
OL,11,FA former church where Take That singer
OL,12,FMark Owen was once said to have been
OL,13,Fan altar server could be transformed
OL,14,Finto a community centre - thanks to a
OL,15,F70-year old piece of artwork.
OL,17,FThe mural, inside the Holy Rosary
OL,18,Fbuilding in Oldham, Greater
OL,19,FManchester, had almost been forgotten
OL,20,Funtil a campaign was launched to get
OL,21,Fit listed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
