OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,FThe work, depicting the crucifixion,
OL,7,Fwas partly painted over by a well-
OL,8,Fmeaning priest in the 1980s and the
OL,9,Fchurch, next to Owen's primary school,
OL,10,Fwas shut in 2017 and targeted by
OL,11,Fvandals.
OL,13,FFormer parishioner Stephen Haines
OL,14,Fexplained: "In 1980, our priest at the
OL,15,Ftime, in an era when Mark Owen of Take
OL,16,FThat was one of our altar servers,
OL,17,Fhe'd over a weekend decided that it
OL,18,Fgot a bit tatty and wanted to paint
OL,19,Fover the mural.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
