CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775488261
OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,F"We've since had experts come in and
OL,7,Fit's restorable subject to finding the
OL,8,Ffunding, and we can restore it to its
OL,9,Foriginal condition.
OL,11,F"So no great damage done. It was
OL,12,Fconcealed but it's still there."
OL,14,FNow a new group has been launched to
OL,15,Ffind long-term use for the building.
OL,17,FThe Oldham Mural & Cultural Heritage
OL,18,FTrust is raising funds to restore the
OL,19,Fmosaic and turn the building into a
OL,20,Fcultural heritage and youth and
OL,21,Fcommunity arts centre for Fitton Hill.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
