OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,FOttilia Ordog, a community
OL,7,Ffacilitator, said: "This will be a
OL,8,Fvibrant, creative space where young
OL,9,Fpeople can express themselves freely,
OL,10,Fdevelop new skills, access creative
OL,11,Factivities and benefit from
OL,12,Fhighquality alternative education
OL,13,Fthrough arts, music and meaningful
OL,14,Fengagement.
OL,26,@nD@IxgnD@LxwoD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
