OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,F"By celebrating a local piece of
OL,7,Finternational artwork, the centre
OL,8,Fwould not only broaden horizons for
OL,9,Fyoung people but also help raise pride
OL,10,Facross the local community,
OL,11,Fstrengthening identity, belonging, and
OL,12,Fcultural connection across Fitton
OL,13,FHill."
OL,15,FLocal resident and fellow trustee Kim
OL,16,FRogers, founder of Spark Oldham,
OL,17,Fadded: "The building has so much
OL,18,Fpotential.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]yD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
