PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775488261
OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,F"I have worked on the estate for over
OL,7,F15 years and seen the need for an
OL,8,Famazing space like this for the
OL,9,Fcommunity, especially the young people.
OL,11,F"If you are a business and you can
OL,12,Fsupport us with bringing this amazing
OL,13,Fspace to life, please get in touch."
OL,15,FHenrietta Billings, director of SAVE
OL,16,FBritain's Heritage, said: "We're
OL,17,Fthrilled that the community has come
OL,18,Ftogether in this way with such passion
OL,19,Fand vision.
OL,26,@uD@dO]xD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
