CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775488261
OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,F"Not only will their plans secure the
OL,7,Ffuture of the building and its
OL,8,Fextraordinary artwork, but they will
OL,9,Falso be providing a fantastic home for
OL,10,Flocal young people to explore their
OL,11,Fown creativity."
OL,13,FThe artwork was created in-situ by
OL,14,FHungarian emigre artist George Mayer-
OL,15,FMarton in 1955 and has been described
OL,16,Fas being "internationally important."
OL,18,FThe artist used a rare combination of
OL,19,Fmosaic and fresco to portray the
OL,20,FCrucifixion, with Christ flanked by
OL,21,Ffigures of Mary and St John.
OL,26,@sD@PO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
