PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775488261
OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,FHistoric England gave the artwork and
OL,7,Fits setting Grade II-listed status in
OL,8,F2022.
OL,10,FMayer-Marton was a leading figure in
OL,11,Fthe Viennese art world in the 1920s
OL,12,Fand 1930s. He and his wife escaped
OL,13,FNazi persecution in 1938, but faced
OL,14,Fanother tragedy in 1940 when an
OL,15,Fincendiary bomb struck their London
OL,16,Fstudio home, destroying most of
OL,17,FGeorge's life's work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
