PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775488261
OL,3,CPlans to transform former church where
OL,4,CTake That singer 'was altar boy'
OL,6,FIn 1952 he was appointed as a lecturer
OL,7,Fat the Liverpool College of Art where
OL,8,Fhe was commissioned by the Roman
OL,9,FCatholic Church to carry out works at
OL,10,Fa number of churches in Lancashire and
OL,11,FCheshire, including the Pentecost,
OL,12,Fwhich now resides in the Metropolitan
OL,13,FChurch of Christ the King in the city.
OL,15,FTristram Hunt, director of the V&A
OL,16,FMuseum in London, said: "The V&A
OL,17,Fregards The Crucifixion... to be a
OL,18,Fremarkable example of post-war mural
OL,19,Fart and the revival of the mosaic in
OL,20,FBritain."
OL,26,@xD@YOU
