OL,6,FNew evidence has concluded that the
OL,7,Ffresco remains intact under the
OL,8,Foverpainting and that it is possible
OL,9,Fto restore the mural to its original
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
